NAME

    Curses-Toolkit - a Curses (text based) Toolkit


DESCRIPTION

    Curses-Toolkit tries to be a modern curses toolkit, to build "graphical"
    console user interfaces easily.

INSTALLATION

    To install this module, run the following commands:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

DEPENDENCIES

    Curses
    Params::Validate

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Curses::Toolkit

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Curses-Toolkit

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Curses-Toolkit

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Curses-Toolkit

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Curses-Toolkit

